data.description: Your new home awaits! Built in 2021 this house still has that new home smell.  No detail was left out on this 3 Bed 2 Bath split bedroom design. White trim throughout matches your custom white kitchen cabinets.  The Kitchen offers all granite counter tops and island as well as all stainless appliances.  Great room features trey ceiling as well as gas fireplace.  Master bedroom features huge walk in closet, double vanity and walk in shower.  Basement is already insulated and stubbed for 3rd bath.  3 car attached garage with extra room for all your toys!  New Lawn installed already so you'll be ready to enjoy this spring. Main floor laundry!
